%I A000663 M1932 N0763 #53 May 16 2026 09:44:24
%S A000663 1,2,9,37,183,933,5314,32043,207212,1415934,10200289,77018442,
%T A000663 607474564,4987909231,42519634303,375395726926,3425423036156,
%U A000663 32245163868760,312631489873499,3117350319650745,31926699391621784,335446169464215478,3611798539160234582,39813272089464106824
%N A000663 Number of binary relations on an infinite set, each with exactly n ordered pairs, up to isomorphism.
%C A000663 See the lowest row in the table given on top of page 66 in the Oberschelp reference.
%D A000663 N. J. A. Sloane, A Handbook of Integer Sequences, Academic Press, 1973 (includes this sequence).
%D A000663 N. J. A. Sloane and Simon Plouffe, The Encyclopedia of Integer Sequences, Academic Press, 1995 (includes this sequence).
%H A000663 Michael Spiegel, <a href="/A000663/b000663.txt">Table of n, a(n) for n = 0..40</a>
%H A000663 W. Oberschelp, <a href="http://gdz.sub.uni-goettingen.de/dms/resolveppn/?PPN=GDZPPN002298732">Kombinatorische Anzahlbestimmungen in Relationen</a>, Math. Ann., 174 (1967), 53-78.
%F A000663 a(s) = [x^s] Sum_{lambda partition of 2s} (1/z_lambda) * Product_{i,j parts of lambda} (1 + x^lcm(lambda_i, lambda_j))^gcd(lambda_i, lambda_j), where z_lambda = Product_k k^c_k * c_k! (c_k = multiplicity of part k in lambda). - _Michael Spiegel_, May 14 2026
%e A000663 The a(2) = 9 relations with 2 edges are:
%e A000663   {1>1, 2>2},
%e A000663   {1>1, 1>2},
%e A000663   {1>1, 2>1},
%e A000663   {1>1, 2>3},
%e A000663   {1>2, 2>1},
%e A000663   {1>2, 1>3},
%e A000663   {1>2, 2>3},
%e A000663   {1>2, 3>2},
%e A000663   {1>2, 3>4}.
%o A000663 (SageMath)
%o A000663 def A000663(s):
%o A000663   R.<x> = PowerSeriesRing(QQ, default_prec=s+1)
%o A000663   n, total = max(2*s, 1), R(0)
%o A000663   for la in Partitions(n):
%o A000663     ed = la.to_exp_dict()
%o A000663     total += prod((1 + x^lcm(i,j))^(gcd(i,j)*ed[i]*ed[j])
%o A000663                  for i in ed for j in ed) / \
%o A000663              prod(k^c * factorial(c) for k, c in ed.items())
%o A000663   return total[s] # _Michael Spiegel_, May 14 2026
%Y A000663 Cf. A000595, A000664, A046858.
%K A000663 nonn,nice
%O A000663 0,2
%A A000663 _N. J. A. Sloane_
%E A000663 a(7)-a(15) from _Vladeta Jovovic_, Jan 10 2000
%E A000663 Terms a(16) and beyond from _Michael Spiegel_, May 14 2026
